{"article_id":"RT3SUTtKR0pRgtxN","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"CIA director nominee John Brennan weathered a barrage of probing questions Thursday ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"as lawmakers pressed for more information about the administration 's rationale for drone strikes against Americans","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"-- with his confirmation potentially hanging in the balance .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Lawmakers ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"after threatening a `` confrontation '' earlier this week over President Obama 's nominees","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"unless they get access to key drone documents ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"used Brennan 's confirmation hearing before the Senate Intelligence Committee","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"to air long-simmering concerns about the issue .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Earlier in the day , senators were allowed to review some of the legal rationale","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"-- released in a bid by the Obama administration","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"to tamp down the controversy .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"But top Democratic lawmakers said Thursday afternoon","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"they want more ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"as Brennan repeatedly defended the program itself .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"`` It 's the idea","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"of giving any president unfettered power","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"to kill an American","depth":14},{"id":17,"text":"without checks and balances","depth":14},{"id":18,"text":"that 's so troubling , ''","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"Sen. Ron Wyden , D-Ore. , said .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"`` Every American has the right","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"to know","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"when their government believes","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"it 's allowed to kill them . ''","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"Wyden said","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"he 's concerned","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"the Justice Department is `` not following through '' on providing `` any and all '' opinions","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"-- aside from what was provided Thursday morning .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"As he did with other senators ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Brennan vowed to do what he could","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"to pry loose that information .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Brennan also said","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"it 's important to speak publicly about the rationale ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"`` people are reacting to a lot of falsehoods","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"that are out there . ''","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"`` We only take such actions as a last resort","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"to save lives","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"when there 's no other alternative , ''","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"he said ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"claiming","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"drone strikes are not ordered","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"to punish terrorists for past attacks .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"Brennan faced bipartisan scrutiny Thursday ,","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"with Democrats pressing him on drones and his views on Bush-era interrogation tactics .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"Republicans , meanwhile , repeatedly questioned him on his knowledge of high-profile security leaks last year .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"Brennan has acknowledged","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"being interviewed as part of an investigation into those leaks ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"but said Thursday","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"he is not a target of that investigation .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"One lawmaker , Sen. Richard Burr , R-N.C. , further threatened to hold up the confirmation over an another issue","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"-- the release of separate documents","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"pertaining to the Benghazi terror attacks .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"On the drones , Committee Chairwoman Dianne Feinstein , D-Calif. , complained","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"that ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"after lawmakers were allowed by the administration to view the classified drone document earlier in the day ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"`` our staff was banned from seeing it . ''","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"`` This is upsetting to a number of members , ''","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"Feinstein tried to get Brennan to commit to ,","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"if confirmed ,","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"working to provide eight additional legal opinions about drone strikes .","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"Brennan sought to ease lawmakers ' concerns .","depth":5},{"id":63,"text":"He said Thursday","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"that being confirmed to the post would be `` the greatest honor of my professional life . ''","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"He also said","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"he understands the `` great interest '' in the legal basis","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"used for killings outside the battlefield of Afghanistan .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"He voiced interest","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"in promoting public discussion on it .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"`` Our system of government and our commitment to transparency deserves nothing less , ''","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Brennan is described as the public face and architect of the targeted-killing program ,","depth":4},{"id":73,"text":"which has expanded under Obama .","depth":4},{"id":74,"text":"Under Brennan , the American cleric Anwar al-Awlaki ,","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"considered a top Al Qaeda operative ,","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"became the first American","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"successfully targeted for death under the program .","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"Two weeks later , his 16-year-old son was also killed in a drone strike ,","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"in which the teen was described as collateral damage .","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"The start of Brennan 's hearing was interrupted several times by protesters from Code Pink .","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"Feinstein briefly suspended the hearing","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"while the protesters were cleared from the room .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"As the hearing resumed ,","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"Brennan also faced continued questions about his views on Bush-era interrogation tactics","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"-- which included waterboarding .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"In an interview with CBS News in 2007 , Brennan defended the program as one","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"that has produced information","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"that 's been `` used against the real hardcore terrorists . ''","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"Brennan has since taken a position against the program","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"and claimed","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"he raised concerns while at the agency .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"He reiterated that point Thursday ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"he raised `` personal objections '' to it ,","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"but did not try to stop the program","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"-- something","depth":15},{"id":97,"text":"he said","depth":15},{"id":98,"text":"was run by other parts of the agency .","depth":14},{"id":99,"text":"He also called waterboarding `` reprehensible . ''","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"A former deputy director at the agency could not confirm , in an interview with Fox News ,","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"that Brennan raised concerns with him .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"Still , the official , John E. McLaughlin , said","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"he supports Brennan 's confirmation","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"and he should be taken at his word .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"`` This was not a program","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"that would normally be discussed between John and myself ,","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"but","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"if he said","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"he talked to colleagues about it ,","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"and expressed reservations ,","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"I believe him ,","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"because this is a very straight-forward , honest guy , ''","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"McLaughlin told Fox News .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"Meanwhile , Feinstein has completed a 6,000-page classified report on the CIA program .","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"Those familiar with its findings tell Fox News","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"it concludes","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"the agency lied about the program 's effectiveness","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"-- a charge","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"denied by those","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"who ran the program .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"Brennan was asked about that report Thursday ,","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"he found some elements of the report `` disturbing . ''","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"On Wednesday , White House Press Secretary Jay Carney defended the nominee .","depth":5},{"id":125,"text":"`` The president believes","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"that John Brennan is uniquely qualified as a 25-year veteran of intelligence work , a 25-year veteran of the CIA ,","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"to lead that agency , ''","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"Carney said .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"`` Mr. Brennan brings ,","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"I think ,","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"not only a vast amount of experience , but a significant perspective on the battles","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"that we wage in this effort","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"and the right way","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"to conduct them . ''","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"Carney said","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"Obama wants the Senate to confirm him `` expeditiously . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":273,"left":208,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":